instructions: Put dinner fork of the table cloth
put the dinner knife to the right of the table cloth
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife
put the soup to the right of the salad knife
put the dessert spoon on the top center of the table cloth
put the dessert spoon to the right of the soup spoon
put the dessert spoon to the far right of the dinner knife
put the dinner place in the center of the table cloth
put the bread plate above the salad fork and to the left of the dessert spoon
put the butter knife on the bread plate
put the wine glass above the soup spoon and behind the dessert spoon
put the water glass to the left of the wine glass
put a napkin on top of the dinner plate
